<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Professional Resume</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .resume {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: auto;
        }
        h1, h2 { color: #2c3e50; }
        ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        hr { border: 1px solid #000; margin: 10px 0; }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .skills-list, .certifications-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .skills-list li, .certifications-list li {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="resume">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>John Doe</h1>
            <p>john.doe@example.com | +1 234 567 890 | 123 Main Street, City, Country</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Skills</h2>
            <ul class="skills-list">
                <li>JavaScript</li><li>Angular</li><li>React</li><li>Node.js</li><li>SQL</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Certifications</h2>
            <ul class="certifications-list">
                <li>AWS Certified Developer</li><li>Google Cloud Associate</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
            <p><strong>Software Engineer - Tech Solutions Inc.</strong></p>
            <p>Jan 2020 - Present</p>
            <p><strong>E-commerce Platform:</strong> Developed a full-stack e-commerce platform with React and Node.js.</p>
            <p><strong>Frontend Developer - Web Innovations</strong></p>
            <p>Jul 2018 - Dec 2019</p>
            <p><strong>Dashboard System:</strong> Built an analytics dashboard using Angular and Chart.js.</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Education</h2>
            <p><strong>ABC University</strong></p>
            <p>B.Sc. in Computer Science | CGPA: 3.8</p>
            <p>2015 - 2019</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Achievements</h2>
            <p>Developed a resume maker tool that automates professional CV generation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>